{"tid":1778322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（Twitter 要人）美國同加拿大議員響人權日不斷提香港！","createTime":"2019-12-11T00:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T18:19:30.000Z","uid":249263,"like":105,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8811d94c557069880ef4e36cde8ff823592e97","tid":1778322,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國時間仲係人權日！<br />\n好多議員陸續出緊Tweets 講香港</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8HQiU6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8HQiU6.png&h=94cb59c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GaAN5z7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGaAN5z7.png&h=94957109&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7LToDU7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7LToDU7.png&h=1dc280e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">快啲去同佢地講下香港被打壓的情況！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝佢地的關注！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同講我地想要一個點樣的香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加番<span style=\"color: red;\"> #humanrights </span>同 <span style=\"color: red;\">#humanrightsday</span><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=2799d98d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task1</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">rt + like + reply</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">老規矩，美加議員仲出緊tweets，所以請用twitter help bot 拎tweets先，佢地齊哂我會再一次po link<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f109050a553925845a0d51fbedb869f188a2cd05","tid":1778322,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:41:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4e62207044820f05b9bb4e3242e2b6910cc960c5","tid":1778322,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:41:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0624af2dafdaf764235598fe55aff0dd2a146dca","tid":1778322,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:41:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"25985fb71708d6650f4b9b26689eb75bde95cefb","tid":1778322,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e5ba0e103435c459453ea775a98a2d12e6ab7600","tid":1778322,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:43:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73a26af8ab11113d9eeeb3fd6e1e5b9a9cddf322","tid":1778322,"uid":264873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T00:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xz19zv9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxz19zv9.jpg&h=28d8eba3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9be334eb70d5f4ba618cc8b6c072d7f0190960fd","tid":1778322,"uid":264873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201